## Decisions and Action Items

* **Adoption Call:** The working group will initiate a formal adoption call on the mailing list for the SRv6 addressing recommendations draft (`draft-horn-srv6ops-addressing-recommendations` / slide slot 3.3).
* **Feedback Gathering:** The authors of `draft-ietf-srv6ops-srv6-deployment` will seek formal feedback from the BESS working group regarding the VXLAN-to-SRv6 migration text before progressing the document to WGLC.

